snippet.title: The Witcher: Rise of the White Wolf Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: The Witcher: Rise of the White Wolf, coming Fall 2009 to Xbox 360 and PLAYSTATION3 courtesy of CD Projekt RED and Atari. Check out this ultra-cool cinematic trailer from Platige Image and Oscar-nominated director Tomasz Baginski, then visit http://www.thewitcher.com to find out more about the game, sign up for the newsletter, download desktop wallpapers and screenshots, and get involved in the community!
